<p class="h1">BERYL</p>
<p class="fl">Hard, lustrous mineral of various colors, mentioned in the Bible as a gemstone (<a href="?bref=Exod.28.20">Ex 28:20</a>; <a href="?bref=Rev.21.20">Rv 21:20</a>). <span class="ital">See</span> <a href="?item=MineralsandMetals_Article_TyndaleOpenBibleDictionary">Minerals and Metals</a>; <a href="?item=StonesPrecious_Article_TyndaleOpenBibleDictionary">Stones, Precious</a>.</p>
